data.description: POOL HOME, NO HOA, & NO FLOOD Zone! This 3-bedroom, 1 bathroom block home sits on almost an acre of land. With a metal roof and updated double paned windows. Stainless steel appliances. Updated bathroom and kitchen in 2019. Vinyl flooring throughout. The property is fully fenced and has 3 sheds offering plenty of storage. Very secluded, the home is at the end of a street and has no neighbors to one side.  Set up your private showing today, before it is gone!
